These scripts were used to make the ROC curves from the ChromHMM posterior probability files.

Annotate_ChromHMM_Bins.R 
Creates bed files for the 200bp windows for each chromosome

ROC_calc_main.R
Loops through all samples and initializes variables and saves data to output.
Calls ROC_calc.R

ROC_calc.R
Calculates the mean of the sum of the posterior probabilities for  states 9, 10, 13, 14,15 and 18  for all true positive or true negative segments.